data.description: Welcome to this charming sugarplum cottage in downtown Wilmington! This adorable home is located within walking distance of the popular Cargo district's bars, restaurants, and shopping. You'll love the off-street parking and the front porch that welcomes you in true southern tradition. Step inside and you'll be greeted by the vintage feel of the living area opening to the kitchen with its white shaker style cabinetry, tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and a dining area for sit-down meals. With three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this updated home boasts refinished hardwood floors, modern windows, bathtubs, and fixtures. The backyard is fully fenced for privacy, and you will appreciate the fresh new sod.  No worries about rain as the roof was replaced in October 2023. The cottage was inspected in March 2023, and every repair suggested has been addressed and is covered by a 2-10 home warranty. Home is currently acting as a successful Airbnb with 4.8 rating. Fully furnished is an option.
